{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "爱如流星 家人的条件",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "莫尔提斯先与拉米艾尔擦肩而过，\\n后又恰好错过了与奈文的相遇。\\n伊莉雅则发现了拉米艾尔。\\n四人皆已意识到对方的存在。\\n然而意外发生，少年趁着夜色跑向了雪山。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "本以为人不在镇上的话\\n肯定藏在山上……\\n可这完全不是能住人的环境啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "对方也有可能用魔法设了\\n结界来藏身。不过无论如何，\\n现在我们都束手无策了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "算了，\\n先和奈文会合再说吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "（也不知道他能不能\\n照顾好那孩子……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "（过去的小不点现在也能照顾孩子了……\\n呵呵，人的成长真是快啊。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "（这魔力……是怎么回事！？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "二位！请稍等一下——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "不见了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "（如此强大的魔力……难以想象持有者\\n会是人类……刚才的究竟是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "他好像已经走了……\\n你可以出来了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "刚才那位是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我也不清楚。\\n但他突然向我们搭话，显得非常可疑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊……艾莉雅让我保护你。\\n我自然要做好才是。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "呵呵，听上去就像是\\n听妈妈嘱咐的乖孩子呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "你们应该不是姐弟吧？\\n是恋人吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我们既不是姐弟也不是恋人，\\n我们虽然没有血缘关系，但却是家人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "这样啊……\\n也会有这种形式的家人啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "嗯。\\n对我来说，没有人比她更重要。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "嗯？这个包裹是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120064_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾丽泽",
            "context": "像是礼物呢。\\n是谁掉在这里的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "也许弄丢的人正在找它。\\n我们去前面的广场问问看吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "星龙祭啊……\\n说来……呵呵。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "嗯？怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "啊，抱歉。想起点事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "拉米艾尔……就是和我在一起的\\n那个龙，相当于是我的父亲。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "他一直都工作很忙，\\n我们在一起相处的时间不多。\\n所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "有一年我们约好了一起过星龙祭。\\n毕竟我当时也就是个小鬼。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "不过不走运的是拉米艾尔接了一桩\\n要出远门的工作，我就想这下没戏了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "所以我放弃了，那晚早早睡下。\\n结果……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "结果？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "早上醒来的时候，\\n拉米艾尔正趴在我的床边睡觉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "他为了成全我的任性，\\n自己通宵飞回来了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "他平时总是一副游刃有余的样子，\\n那天却伤痕累累、精疲力尽。我惊讶\\n他竟做到这份上，甚至感觉有些好笑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "你当时高兴吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "是啊……我很高兴。\\n有种自己被人珍视的感觉，\\n让我也想要去珍惜他。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "那天我们一起吃了饭，\\n我记得他好像还给我买了礼物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "阿尔夫，你难道没有\\n想要一起过星龙祭的人吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "怎么又不说话了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "为什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "嗯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "你们为什么是父子呢？\\n一个是人一个是龙……\\n明明没有血缘关系啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "就算有血缘关系\\n也未必就能是父子吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "这世上有很多\\n没有血缘关系的父母和孩子。\\n虽说我们的确有些特殊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "可是，果然还是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "嗯？你为什么如此\\n执着于血缘关系？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿尔夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "在镇上转了一圈却毫无线索。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "（不过，既然炼狱之匙，\\n肯定早就被各种势力盯上，\\n有所戒备也是意料之中……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "不过我还真搞不懂……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "（梅奈为什么\\n不惜制作炼狱之匙这种东西\\n也要留下炼狱文书呢……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "（炼狱文书到底是什么呢……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯？那……那不是天使吗？\\n应该是隶属北部教会的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "原来如此……北部教会也\\n掌握了炼狱之匙的情报了吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "看来这次的事情\\n不会那么简单就结束呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "当天夜晚",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "在镇上感受到异样的魔力？\\n那魔力的主人有可能是\\n炼狱之匙的主人吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "不能排除这个可能。\\n但也有可能是某种非人之物……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "你是说有怪物混进城镇里？\\n我可不想碰见这种麻烦事啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "目前还没有有力的线索。\\n这样下去任务就要以失败告终了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "刚才的声音是？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "难道是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "糟糕！阿尔夫不见了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "喂喂，这么深更半夜的跑哪儿去……\\n而且外面……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "在这种天气里乱跑简直就是自杀！\\n而且看这脚印……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "嗯，向雪山的方向去了。\\n我们追，拉米艾尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210132_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉米艾尔",
            "context": "好。雪山栖息着很多魔兽，\\n切勿大意，奈文！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110365_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈文",
            "context": "知道啦！我们走吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22903_02_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}